# Dependency management (Go Modules)
# The 'vendor/' directory is typically ignored if you are using Go Modules
# and want to rely on the `go.mod` and `go.sum` for dependency management.
# However, some projects might choose to commit the vendor directory for specific reasons.
vendor/

# Environment specific files
.env
.local
